00:40:10.510 --> 00:40:12.410
And especially
the arowana world.

00:40:12.410 --> 00:40:14.470
It's a very masculine fish.

00:40:14.470 --> 00:40:17.020
And all the hobbyists
that I met were

00:40:17.020 --> 00:40:20.810
men with maybe one exception.

00:40:20.810 --> 00:40:22.550
And also I was writing
about the history

00:40:22.550 --> 00:40:23.740
of exploration and science.

00:40:23.740 --> 00:40:25.712
And so also a very
male dominated.

00:40:25.712 --> 00:40:26.920
KELLY BAILEY: Male dominated.

00:40:26.920 --> 00:40:28.919
EMILY VOIGT: But there
were these two characters

00:40:28.919 --> 00:40:33.110
that I think spoke to me.

00:40:33.110 --> 00:40:37.890
So one was in the 1850s-- this
Austrian explorer, Ida Pfeiffer

00:40:37.890 --> 00:40:42.255
who discovered the lake--
or is often credited,

00:40:42.255 --> 00:40:45.450
at least, with discovering the
lake where the super red comes

00:40:45.450 --> 00:40:46.740
from in the heart of Borneo.

00:40:46.740 --> 00:40:48.970
So she was a housewife.

00:40:48.970 --> 00:40:51.340
And she raised two sons.

00:40:51.340 --> 00:40:53.450
And she was a piano teacher.

00:40:53.450 --> 00:40:55.930
And she just had
dreams of traveling.

00:40:55.930 --> 00:40:58.660
And when they were fully grown--
when her sons were fully grown,

00:40:58.660 --> 00:40:59.797
she just took off.

00:40:59.797 --> 00:41:01.380
She told them she
was going to Brazil.

00:41:01.380 --> 00:41:02.963
But she didn't tell
them she was going

00:41:02.963 --> 00:41:04.850
to go home the long way around.

00:41:04.850 --> 00:41:08.190
So she circumambulated the
globe, which at that time

00:41:08.190 --> 00:41:11.440
would be like being
gone for two years.

00:41:11.440 --> 00:41:14.406
She was really an
extraordinary woman.

00:41:14.406 --> 00:41:16.919
And so I admire her a lot.

00:41:16.919 --> 00:41:18.460
And then there's
another model, which

00:41:18.460 --> 00:41:20.043
is Heiko's mother,
where you just take

00:41:20.043 --> 00:41:22.300
the kids to the jungle, right?

00:41:22.300 --> 00:41:24.967
So those things
are all on my mind.

