about something closer to home.

00:41:43.933 --> 00:41:46.860
So it's about my bird feeder,
which sounds incredibly boring,

00:41:46.860 --> 00:41:49.966
but let me warn you that
pet fish also sounded boring

00:41:49.966 --> 00:41:52.090
when I told everybody I
was writing about pet fish.

00:41:52.090 --> 00:41:53.730
And they were not.

00:41:53.730 --> 00:41:57.310
I live on the 25th floor of an
apartment building in New York.

00:41:57.310 --> 00:42:01.290
So it's kind of hard
to have a bird feeder

00:42:01.290 --> 00:42:03.050
because if you put it
outside the window,

00:42:03.050 --> 00:42:04.508
it's going to fall
and kill people.

00:42:04.508 --> 00:42:07.420
So I found one that
goes inside-- the bird

00:42:07.420 --> 00:42:09.530
comes inside the house.

00:42:09.530 --> 00:42:13.437
And initially, the guy who
sold it to me up in Maine

00:42:13.437 --> 00:42:15.270
was like, you're not
going to get any birds.

00:42:15.270 --> 00:42:17.940
And we ended up getting
some house finches.

00:42:17.940 --> 00:42:20.390
Now, this connects
back to this fish story

00:42:20.390 --> 00:42:25.030
because there's a whole
elaborate saga of what happened

00:42:25.030 --> 00:42:26.860
with the house finches.

00:42:26.860 --> 00:42:31.810
Spoiler alert, a hawk ate
one in our living room.

00:42:31.810 --> 00:42:33.729
But it turns out that
the house finches

00:42:33.729 --> 00:42:35.020
are an introduced species here.

00:42:35.020 --> 00:42:37.780
They were brought
over in the pet trade

00:42:37.780 --> 00:42:41.680
from the west coast in
1940, I think it was.

00:42:41.680 --> 00:42:44.570
And just a few of them were
released on Long Island

00:42:44.570 --> 00:42:48.990
because the dealer knew that
it was illegal to have them.

00:42:48.990 --> 00:42:49.880
And he got worried.

00:42:49.880 --> 00:42:50.880
And so he released them.

00:42:50.880 --> 00:42:53.213
And now there's like a billion
of them on the east cost.

00:42:55.555 --> 00:42:58.320
I think that this book certainly
has informed the way that I

00:42:58.320 --> 00:42:59.880
just look at every animal now.

00:42:59.880 --> 00:43:04.887
And that may be my
next pet trade subject.

