00:46:09.630 --> 00:46:12.230
Arowana are super picky lovers.

00:46:12.230 --> 00:46:15.350
They insist upon
picking their own mate.

00:46:15.350 --> 00:46:17.360
They wont just mate
with any other fish.

00:46:20.600 --> 00:46:24.660
Actually, a surprising
number remain mated for life.

00:46:24.660 --> 00:46:28.520
So you could.

00:46:28.520 --> 00:46:30.900
But I don't know
how you're going

00:46:30.900 --> 00:46:32.700
to get the fish into the US.

00:46:32.700 --> 00:46:38.167
And I would warn you against
going down this path.

